PL Grado ETSII ULL Lab: Infix to Postfix translator. 
Includes if the else statements.

Simple example in the client using jison.
Uses jquery. Be sure you modify "main.js" so
that "jquery.js" is found.

run "rake" to produce "calculator.js"

Contents of ~/bin/jsbeautify:

node ~/node_modules/beautifier/bin/beautifier.js $1

install package:
  sudo npm install beautifier

  more about beautifier:
  https://github.com/rickeyski/node-beautifier
